com.intrasonics

Class Error

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intrasonics.Error
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EventEngineResponse, HeartbeatError

    public class Error
extends java.lang.Object
    The base class for Decoder or Decoder Engine errors.

    This class should be subclassed to represent specific errors.

    • Field Summary

      A timestamp specifying the number of milliseconds since the UNIX epoch (1970-01-01 00:00:00) that the error occurred
